    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my reliable ride. It\u2019s been a fantastic car for me and is still in really solid shape, perfect for anyone who needs a dependable set of wheels that looks great on the road. It's been well-cared for and drives like a dream\u2014I'm honestly going to miss it! If you're looking for a quality car at a fair price, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 32500.0,
